Slicer
-- A Valgrind tool by Anthony Carno

Build/installation (from Valgrind docs):

    1) cd <valgrind>
    2) autogen.sh
    3) ./configure --prefix=`pwd`/inst
    4) make
    5) make install

Running:
    <valgrind>/inst/bin/valgrind --tool=slicer <options> <program>

Options:
    --funcs=<FILENAME>      Only profile functions included in <FILENAME>
                                (1 function/line) (HIGHLY RECOMMENDED)
    --output=<FILENAME>     Output to <FILENAME> (in CSV format)


    
